General.Name: Indus Energy Nl
General.Description: Industrial Minerals Ltd, a mineral exploration company, explores for and develops mineral projects in Australia. The company primarily explores for gypsum and salt, silica sand, construction sand, and aggregates. It holds 100% interests in 14 high purity silica sand projects and 6 industrial mineral projects in Western Australia. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is headquartered in Peppermint Grove, Australia.
